What is CSS ?
CSS stabds for Cascading Style Sheets
HTML i sbackbone of your website but its ugly.
CSS lets us create beautiful and modern looking websites.
CSS does not control the functionality of the site.So if you want to click a button and have it do something that will require JavaScript.
CSS can be written in 3 different ways.
    Inline with the style HTML attribute
    Internal with the <style> element
    External .css file

How does CSS work?
CSS is simply a layer on top of HTML.
We'll always need to write HTML to make a website,but technicall CSS is optional



